          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The differential  cross  section  for   the   2H(g,n)",
                " reaction was measured at Maxlab using tagged photons",
                " of 10 - 70 MeV energy.  This measurement may be used",
                " to check the cross sections of a (g,n) reactions, as",
                " the two-body photodisintegration  cross  section  of",
                " deuterium is a well-known. The results were compared",
                " with a calculation made from  a  parametrization  of",
                " all available data."
              ]
            }
          ],
